<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title> 예약 정보 확인 </title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
	<div class="flex center" style="width: 50%; min-width: 600px;">
		<article class="card flex col" style="width: 100%;">
			<section class="borderB" style="background-color: var(--black); color: #fff; padding: 2rem 2rem 1.8rem;">
				<h1>예약 정보 확인</h1>
			</section>
			<section class="flex">
				<div style="flex: 1; border-right: 1px solid var(--black);">
					<img src="<%= movie.img %>" 
						onerror="this.src='<%= movie.subImg %>'; this.onerror=null;"> 
				</div>
				<div class="flex col" style="flex: 1; font-size: 1.4rem;">
					<div class="content borderB" style="text-align: center;">
						<h2><%= movie.name %></h2>  
					</div>
					<div class="content borderB">
						<h3 style="border-bottom: 2px solid var(--black); display: inline-block;">접수된 좌석 번호</h3>
						<p class="tag" style="margin: 1.6rem auto 0; font-weight: bold;"><%= seatNo %></p>
					</div>
					<div class="content borderB" style="text-align: center;">
						무료 관람 신청이 접수되었습니다 ✨
					</div>
					<form action="/" class="flex center content" style="height: 100%;">
						<button type="submit" class="tag" style="width: 100%; font-size: 1.4rem; background-color: var(--accent);">처음으로 돌아가기</button>
					</form>
				</div>
		</article>
	</div>
</body>

</html>